ZH: 我们需要进行一次表决来决定下一步的行动。
EN: We need to have a vote to decide on the next course of action.

ZH: 请所有参与者在表决中严格遵守规则。
EN: Please all participants adhere strictly to the rules during the vote.

ZH: 在表决之前，请大家仔细考虑所有选项。
EN: Before the vote, please carefully consider all options.

ZH: 这个提案需要通过三分之二的表决才能生效。
EN: This proposal requires a two-thirds majority vote to pass.

ZH: 表决结果将在会议结束后公布。
EN: The vote results will be announced after the meeting.

ZH: 我们将通过无记名表决来得到真实的意见。
EN: We will use an anonymous vote to get honest feedback.

ZH: 请将你的表决结果写在纸上并递给主席。
EN: Please write down your vote on paper and hand it to the chairperson.

ZH: 每个人都有权利在表决中发表自己的意见。
EN: Everyone has the right to voice their opinion during the vote.

ZH: 我们在今晚的聚会上将进行关于年度预算的表决。
EN: We will have a vote on the annual budget at tonight's gathering.

ZH: 表决结果将直接影响我们的未来发展方向。
EN: The vote results will directly impact our future direction.

ZH: 请尊重每个人参与表决的权利。
EN: Please respect everyone's right to participate in the vote.

ZH: 我们必须尽快就这个问题进行表决。
EN: We must vote on this issue as soon as possible.

ZH: 否决的表决结果将导致提案被否决。
EN: A negative vote result will lead to the proposal being rejected.

ZH: 请在表决前讨论相关议题。
EN: Please discuss the relevant topics before the vote.

ZH: 表决应该是一个公平公正的过程。
EN: The vote should be a fair and just process.

ZH: 我们将通过手举形式进行表决。
EN: We will vote by a show of hands.

ZH: 请用红色笔在表决单上标明你的选择。
EN: Please mark your choice on the vote slip with a red pen.

ZH: 表决结果将是大家共同的决定。
EN: The vote result will be a collective decision.

ZH: 请尽快进行正式的表决。
EN: Please proceed with the formal vote as soon as possible.
